   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}そ{00}ュ{00}う{00}る{00}え{00}ろ{00}1{00}じ{00}イ{00}用{00}し{00}ニ{00}{01}{00}、{00}·{00}1{00}カ{00}担い{00}り{00}{01}{00}、、Sぁあいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ネハバパ·々ビベブミメちっつぞラてリずン下がー我とぬ開』官きの間ばは機{00}·{00}！戦{00}Mたたな、{00}{01}！ェ{00}M本そな、{00}{01}ぁ……那是！！",
   "zh_hex": "1500420028007f001800480019004a000e0024005000d80023006e000100020004000e005600e40017004700010002021415161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d036f70717204077377757a7c2c2d2e29802f812685891c088b31358d0d8f1d379139389200040006b90013a0243302000106530013482333020001150909e7b7e7b6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x150d",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是之前在非洲交过手的那支部队吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7cdef51ef29e8f0eacde861ef36ef66e7b4e7b7e883ef70e7c9e802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x154c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（泽诺比亚……连你、也在那里吗？）",
   "zh_hex": "150ae984e972e825e7d60909e86ee7b802e7c0ef29e7b7ef31e802050b00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1583",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方MS部队展开！正朝我们这边冲过来{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1efa7ef9eef70e7c9e989e7faef97ef3beaadefcce7bbe7b9e899e95eef36efcf00ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15b5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看样子、对方可不像是来欢迎我们的呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7dae88602e7beefb1e7c4e7b5e8e9e7b6efcfea92e931efcce7bbe7b4e9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e5",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是打算攻击我们吗……托雷斯、MS队、{00}出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7f5e8899ee7cc8be7bbe8020909e7f4e8afe7c8021314e7c90200afe7cc060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15fd",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全机即刻展开队形、迎击来敌！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7e4e855e91fe989e7fae7c9ec6702e931e7ccefcfe7e3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1637",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布莱特舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x163f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台高达、连我们月之民、都未能掌握它{00}的全部底细！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e812ef2b02e86eefcce7bbe850e7cdef3802e840e8b4e7c6eb36eb37e97800e7b4efb4ef70e9b4eb9aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然那台∀高达有了反应、就可以断定、{00}是出状况了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7b7ea16effee812ef2be7cbe7bae87ce87302e7c5e7c4e7f3e982e8670200e7b6efbee98be8d0e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1696",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白、哈利中尉！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e80902e7e8e82ec086060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ad",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "罗兰就这样投入战斗！其余各机严加戒备{00}、迎击敌人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ece86fe7c5e7b9e7dae948e891ef28e7ffef97e8cfeb27e819e7e4eaa1e854eb5ae8770002e931e7cce7e3efb2ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16f5",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1730",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x176d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……月光蝶！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e850e83dea03ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17ab",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……这是何等强烈的压迫感！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7b9e7b6efbce826e8adeaece7b4e992eb70e87def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e1",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这跟之前的对手……完全不是一个层{00}次！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e973e7cdef51e7b4e7beef660909e87eefb4e7b5e7b6efb6e828ebc100e864ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x183f",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！难道、它又复活了不成！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d06e866e82a02e978e8f1e9eee8d4e7bae7b5e837060500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1878",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x189b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布莱特舰长！6点钟方向、出现了新的舰{00}影！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406e9cde822ebf9d09d02afe82fe7baef8ae7b4e7d400ea8e06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18cd",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18fa",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉、那是！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec08602e7b7e7b606050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1928",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那些人是金卡拉姆一族！是执掌月之民武{00}力的家族！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8a4efb2e7b6e902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5eef97e7b6e9fceb36e850e7cdef38e8ec00efb0e7b4e7dfeb5eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1944",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们虽说没有实战经验、战力却在迪安娜{00}回归军之上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe8b8e7ede7d8e7cbe87fef28e8b7ea9902ef28efb0eadfef29ea11e7fce7ea00ef52e947e7e0e7cdef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x195d",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "小心、布莱特舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ee82d02e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1989",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白了、哈利中尉",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809e7ba02e7e8e82ec08600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x199e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全体人员、转入对金卡拉姆舰队的迎击态{00}势！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4ef4fefb2e84902e9c2e891e7bee902e801e7c2e823e7d4e7c9e7b4e931e7cce99400e8fdef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19b3",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方的战力尚是未知数！都给我小心作战{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1e7b4ef28efb0eccee7b6e8b4e85ae914ef97e840e839efcce83ee82def2fef2800ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19ef",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a16",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "第一装甲区块、大破！",
   "zh_hex": "15e940efb6e98febdbef35ec1002efa5ef6def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a23",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、不！这是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b5ef97e7b9e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a34",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是被击毁！是外部装甲、正在遭到分解{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7f1e7cce97cef97e7b6e8f7ef70e98febdb02ef3bef29eb1ee7d7efaee89d00ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a6d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、正是月光蝶……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702ef3be7b6e850e83dea0309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac6",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉！你莫非知道些什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec08606e7b8eba0e8f0e85ae82ae8a4e7dde7bd0605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是、月光蝶……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b602e850e83dea0309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b03",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是、据传曾毁灭了地球文明的、月光蝶{00}系统之光！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b602e8ccea38ea2ae97ce8e1e7baef63efd3ea4eef39e7b402e850e83dea0300e941e929e7cde83def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b40",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毁灭了……地球文明？",
   "zh_hex": "15e97ce8e1e7ba0909ef63efd3ea4eef39050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b74",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『你是谁？』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7b8e7b6e923050d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b85",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『曾被我打倒过的你』",
   "zh_hex": "150cea2ae7f1efcce7f5e848ef36e7b4e7b80d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b9a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『有个已经消失的你』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7cbe828ef3ae8b7e928e8a5e7b4e7b80d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1baf",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『这是为何？』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7b9e7b6e7c1efbc050d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bd8",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "军团、既是全体、亦是个体",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e0ea5e02e8c4e7b6efb4ef4f02efdee7b6e828ef4f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bea",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "万物相连的存在",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f8e99ee8b1e86ee7b4e993ef290000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bfb",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因你是脱离了那完美之环的存在、所以{00}你、必须被废弃……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7b8e7b6e9e5e901e7bae7b7e87ee9f4e7cdef47e7b4e993ef2902e7fbe7f300e7b802e860e9a2e7f1eae5e93809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c39",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『我吗？』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefcce802050d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c60",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为恶的军团、容不下异分子……您、也请{00}去安息吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dee7b4e7e0ea5e02ed2fe7b589eb32cde8860909e83502e7c0e83a00e7ebe7fcec6ae7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cd2",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……凯利、你手臂上的伤、不要紧吧？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e95fe82e02e7b8aeee92b2e7b4e8f902e7b5ef2aeaede7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cff",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈、不过少了条手臂、算不得什么大事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e802e7b5ef36eface7bae9d4ef66ee9202e889e7b5e80ae7dde7bdefa5efb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d0f",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一想到能与你并肩作战、这点伤、就根本{00}算不上什么",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e7e6e7d7e7c6e832e7b8e957eb16ef2fef2802e7b9e822e8f902e7c5e9b8efa600e889e7b5ef4ce7dde7bd0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d45",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵……这还真是你的作风",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d0909e7b9e7f7e820e7b6e7b8e7b4ef2feb750000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d6d",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是我们重新选择的道路、就并肩战斗到{00}最后吧、卡多！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b68be7bbe8a1ef8ae966eaaae7b4e82ae8d202e7c5e957eb16ef28e7ffe7d700e8c5e7fee7d002e801e7e90600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dbf",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、凯利……与你并肩到底！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e95fe82e0909e832e7b8e957eb16e7d7e9b4060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1df5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、我们是成功把敌人击退了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02efcce7bbe7b6e837e9b1e81be7e3efb2e7cce880e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e2a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布莱特舰长！那颗小行星上、有通信传来{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406e7b7eec7e83e9fb5b202e7cbc2e90fea38d900060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e5a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……通信？究竟是谁发来的？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef59e90f05e906ef2ce7b6e923e870efcfe7b4050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e85",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这个嘛……对方自称、是迪安娜·索雷尔{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e828e9360909e7bed0abea0102e7b6ea11e7fce7ea04e93ce8afe7e10009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eb5",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜·索雷尔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7ea04e93ce8afe7e1060500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ee4",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托雷斯、另一位自称迪安娜女王的人物、{00}收容得怎么样了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e8afe7c802e99b87e834abea01ea11e7fce7eab0e884e7b4b4e99e0200e926ed2fe80ae7f2e7bde7dae7ba05000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f1f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗大尉已乘联络艇前去迎接、想必{00}很快就能抵达这边",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6ef3aebb1ef2eeb14eb6bef51e7ebe931efce02e7e6e86000e981e85fe7c5e7c6e96eef2be7b9e8990000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f59",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜女王……吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7eaefade8840909e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哟、这不是哈利中尉吗？在这种地方、做{00}什么呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb2c02e7b9e7b5e7b6e7e8e82ec086e80205ef29e7b9e7d1bfd002e81c00e7dde7bde90705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd1",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这毛病、是偶尔才犯的……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b9eb60ed8b02e7b6ea85e7e1e836eb0ee7b409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ffa",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x201c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有时候、连我自己、都会厌恶起自己将要{00}去做的事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cbef2dea3902e86eefccefb5e8c902e840e7e2eb2be7dee847efb5e8c9e84aef2a00e7ebe81ce7b4efb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2059",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哈？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e8050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x208f",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔哇！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81dea88ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e3",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……琪耶尔小姐",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa1ea31e7e1e83ee9210000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x210d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x212b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？哈利中尉和迪安娜女王、都不见{00}了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0605e7e8e82ec086e7d3ea11e7fce7eab0e88402e840e7b5e85c00e7ba060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2164",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉的斯摩也不见了、看来中尉{00}他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec086e7b4e7c8ee35e7c0e7b5e85ce7ba02e7f6d9c08600e80c090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21a4",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……布莱特舰长、我已经把迪安娜女王带{00}来了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e831e846e7cfe7d4ef34028bef3ae8b7e81bea11e7fce7eab0e884e93700d9e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21d2",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！是哈利中尉回来了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15090906e7b6e7e8e82ec0868cd9e7bae80206050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2202",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉？他、出什么事了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec08605e80c02afe7dde7bda9e7bae80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2231",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……对了、是那位在小行星上的迪安娜{00}女王啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7bee7ba02e7b6e7b7e834ef29e83eefd6ef69ef4ce7b4ea11e7fce7ea00efade884e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2248",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的……！这到底、是怎么一回事{00}啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b4090906e7b9e7d7e9b402e7b6e7f2e7bd878ca900e7c30909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x227b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、你们这边、也是诸事缠身呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e7b8e7bbe7b9e89902e7c0e7b6ea56efb8ec34e88de9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22ab",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22db",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是迪安娜·索雷尔、月之民的女王",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6ea11e7fce7ea04e93ce8afe7e102e850e7cdef38e7b4b0e8840000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2307",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、刚才消失的那位、是个叫琪耶尔{00}·海姆的少女？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e8bce836e928e8a5e7b4e7b7e83402e7b6e828e8c1efa1ea31e7e100ef4be91be823e7b4efacefad050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x233e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想必没错、琪耶尔小姐、与迪安娜女王长{00}得一模一样",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6e860e7d8e88502efa1ea31e7e1e83ee92102e832ea11e7fce7eaefade884ef3400e80aefb6ea91efb6e7da0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x235e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也无法确定她究竟是哪一位、便一直瞒{00}着各位……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0e7dce84ee88ce867e88ee906ef2ce7b6e8ffefb6e83402e8faefb6e875ec8000e86de819e83409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x239a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、在这里的这位、确实就是真正的迪{00}安娜女王没错吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef29e7b9ef31e7b4e7b9e83402e88ce87fe7c5e7b6e820ef3be7b4ea1100e7fce7eaefade884e7d8e885e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d4",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、我千真万确就是迪安娜本人",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602efcceafde820e9f8e88ce7c5e7b6ea11e7fce7eaefa6efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2401",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "话说回来、哈利中尉、究竟为何要带走琪{00}耶尔小姐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81fe7ed8cd902e7e8e82ec08602e906ef2ce7c18aef2ae937e890efa100ea31e7e1e83ee921090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2435",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恐怕、是为了牵制阿格里帕吧",
   "zh_hex": "15eb33e95802e7b6e7c1e7baeb94e8dee7d2e824ef31eb01e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2466",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿格里帕？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e824ef31eb01050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2487",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他是执掌月球政务的、门提纳家族的人",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7b6e9fceb36e850efd3ea68e94fe7b402e90ce821e882e7dfeb5ee7b4efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x249b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我下到地球的这段时间、曾把月球的统治{00}、托付给了他……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef4de7d7ef63efd3e7b4e7b9ea6bef2de8fc02ea2ae81be850efd3e7b4e929ea790002e7f4e97ee839e7bae80c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24d5",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "似乎另有隐情",
   "zh_hex": "15e944e933e99be7cbeb73e88b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24ff",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是、那个人、似乎在月球上谋划着什{00}么",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b602e7b7e828efb202e944e933ef29e850efd3ef4cea6eea74e86de7dd00e7bd0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2519",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "解开倒X封印的、想必也是那个人在背后{00}指使",
   "zh_hex": "15e89de7fae848eed9eb83ec4fe7b402e7e6e860e7c0e7b6e7b7e828efb2ef29e9e4e7fe00e8c0e83f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2553",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倒X……就是刚才出现的、那架胸口有伤{00}的MS吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e848eed90909e7c5e7b6e8bce836afe82fe7b402e7b7e99dee8ceabde7cbe8f900e7b41314e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x258b",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是据传、曾给地球文明带来过毁灭的{00}MS之一",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8ccea3802ea2ae839ef63efd3ea4eef39e937efcfef36e97ce8e1e7b400efa7ef9ee7cdefb60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25cb",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看刚才那股力量、这话倒也不见得是空穴{00}来风",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e8bce836e7b7edacdae85102e7b9e81fe848e7c0e7b5e85ce80ae7b6e93fef0e00d9eb7500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25fe",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是属于我们的过去……于你们而言、却{00}相当于未来",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6ea24e879efcce7bbe7b4ef36e7eb0909e879e7b8e7bbe89cefd702eadf00e8b1ef53e879e8b4efcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x261a",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个斗争的时代、我们称之为黑历史、想{00}必各位也有所耳闻",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828e7ffe852e7b4ef2de8e702efcce7bbea01e7cde7c1ef3ee8fbe92502e7e600e860e819e834e7c0e7cbe7fbee89ebac0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x263a",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "据说那台倒X和∀高达、都是在那全盛时{00}期建造出来的",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cce7ede7b7ea16e848eed9e7d3effee812ef2b02e840e7b6ef29e7b7efb4ee72ef2d00eac9ea61e93eefbeefcfe7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2678",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "∀高达……",
   "zh_hex": "15effee812ef2b09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x269b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆那个家伙……搬出那样的MS、{00}究竟想做什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823e7b7e828e7dfe7fd0909ecddefbee7b7e7dae7b4efa7ef9e0200e906ef2ce7e6e81ce7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26db",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他和那支来历不明的部队、似乎也并非素{00}不相识……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7d3e7b7e883efcfe8fbe7b5ef39e7b4ef70e7c902e944e933e7c0e957e8f0ec8600e7b5e8b1e92f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2721",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……眼下、还是该避免妄加猜测、毕竟我{00}们手头的情报太少了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e90bef4d02e7f7e7b6e898efd9eb7decc6e854ee65eace02ea2cef2cefcc00e7bbef66e92ee7b4e88be913e86aeface7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2741",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正我们本就在前往月球的途中、不如就{00}这样直接赶路过去吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3befcce7bbefa6e7c5ef29ef51e911e850efd3e7b4ebf5ef4e02e7b5e7f0e7c500e7b9e7dae875efceea04e8d2ef36e7ebe7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x277d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也好……只要到了月球、就能和阿纳海姆{00}公司取得联系了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c70909ef32ef2ae7d7e7bae850efd302e7c5e7c6e7d3e7d2e882e91be82300e9a4eafee987e80aef2ee941e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27b4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利的事固然让我担心、阿格里帕的图谋{00}、也同样令我放心不下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ee7b4a9eac0e7efe7f98be9fde82d02e7d2e824ef31eb01e7b4eb2dea6e0002e7c0e85de7dae94e8be86ce82de7b589000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可以的话、还请允许我、随各位一同前往{00}月球",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e7f7e83aecade8a7efcc02e9a1e819e834efb6e85def51e91100e850efd30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2809",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当然、没问题",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e7ef02e7d8e997ea120000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2832",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就这么定了、我们就这样直奔月球而去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b9e7bde867e7ba02efcce7bbe7c5e7b9e7dae875ed49e850efd3e89ce7eb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2864",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "逃走的那个试作体吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c2e890e7b4e7b7e828e91def2fef4fe80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x288c",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本是因能力不足、理应被废弃的个体、可{00}它的力量却远超预想……",
   "zh_hex": "15d2e7b6ef33e7c6dae7b5ea1e02e872e873e7f1eae5e938e7b4e828bc02e7c400e978e7b4dae851eadfe94ceaf6ea5ae7e60909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28c8",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28e9",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对于拥有它的那支奥古、我们必须采取些{00}对策才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee879eb35e7cbe978e7b4e7b7e883e82be84d02efcce7bbe860e9a2ec9ee987e8a400e7beebe4e836efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x290a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不如就请示那位大人、由他来定夺……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7f0e7c5e83aeab0e7b7e834efa5efb202e8a6e80cefcfe867ea1709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2936",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不行！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5efd6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2943",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "区区这点小事、岂能去惊扰那位大人的心{00}神",
   "zh_hex": "15ef35ef35e7b9e822e83ea902eac3e7c6e7ebec6debc7e7b7e834beb4e7b4e82d00e9aa0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2961",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个所谓的试作体、放着不管便是",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828e7fbe92be7b4e91def2fef4f02e86ce86de7b5e93be8fae7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2991",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29b3",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把它当成障碍、才是不妥、既有那等力量{00}、就这么毁掉岂不可惜",
   "zh_hex": "15e81be978c4e837ebfce8c602e836e7b6e7b5ee0502e8c4e7cbe7b7e826dae8510002e7c5e7b9e7bde97ce9d3eac3e7b5e7c4e9c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29d6",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就当是暂时寄放在奥古那里……这么想便{00}好了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5c4e7b6e9ffef2de803e86cef29e82be84de7b7ef310909e7b9e7bde7e6e8fa00e7c7e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ef",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对……一直到那时机降临的那一瞬为止",
   "zh_hex": "15e7be0909efb6e875e7d7e7b7ef2de7e4e943ed1ee7b4e7b7efb6ebdfe7c1e8690000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7aea",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不妙！这艘舰要是被击毁、那可就糟{00}了……！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ecc706e7b9eb18e7d4ef2ae7b6e7f1e7cce97c02e7b7e7c4e7c5eeaf00e7ba09090600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cd6",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？迪安娜女王她！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705ea11e7fce7eaefade884e88eef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d01",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！恐怕、是亲卫队在里头接应！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97eb33e95802e7b6e894e9b2e7c9ef29ef31e92eefcee873ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d2f",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不妙！无论如何、都要把她找出来！{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5ecc7ef97e7dce8dce7f0efbc02e840ef2ae81be88ee9d2efbeefcfef9700ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d6b",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜女王、请您快些！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7eaefade88402e83ae835e85fe8a4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7da4",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dc2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……情况如何？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88be8d0e7f0efbc050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dec",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不行！对方、还在紧追不舍！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5efd6ef97e7beefb102e7f7ef29eaede8dde7b5eb17ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e26",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哇！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea88ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e30",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那帮家伙……难道明知迪安娜大人就{00}在舰上吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e910e7dfe7fd0909e866e82aef39e85aea11e7fce7eabeb4e7c500ef29e7d4b2e8020605000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e76",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……无妨、开火",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dce97f02e7fae8da0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e9d",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "f5"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e9e",
   "jp_len": 42,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1533020002061a0213a0243302000106ab001348233302000115e7c4e7deef97e9d0ec1ee7b4e8b9efbee9b1e9e102e9780909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7eea",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这就脱离、迪安娜大人！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e7c5e9e5e90102ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f1e",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们出来了！别让她跑了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbefbeefcfe7baef97e7e5e7f9e88eeb6fe7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f52",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、看招啊啊啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e7f6e97ae7c3e7c3e7c3060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f86",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是现在！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fb6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "糟了！",
   "zh_hex": "15eeafe7ba06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fe6",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "终究、还是让她给逃掉了呢……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e2e90602e7f7e7b6e7f9e88ee839e8c2e9d3e7bae90709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8011",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是……万分抱歉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b60909e9f8efaee922e9270000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x803d",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不必谢罪、当务之急、是尽快重新抓回女{00}王",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e860e8b2ea7f02ef53e94fe7cdea6202e7b6e8f2e85fe8a1ef8ae962ef52efad00e8840000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x808d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "组建突入部队！立即突入内部、把女王…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15ea0dea61e8b6e891ef70e7c9ef97e86be855e8b6e891e99aef7002e81befade8840900090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80d2",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看来、我和那支部队、还真是有缘呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6efcf02efcce7d3e7b7e883ef70e7c902e7f7e820e7b6e7cbecf9e9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8103",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如何处置？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efbce903ea0e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x812a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那就把他们清除掉、毕竟那股力量、{00}迟早会成为阻碍",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c5e81be80ce7bbe995e974e9d302ea2cef2ce7b7edacdae8510200ea10e963e7e2e837e7c1e8efe8c6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x815d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x818a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……罗兰？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ece86f050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81ad",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我还没下令让∀高达出击呢！怎么了、罗{00}兰！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f7e7d8ef4de94ee7f9effee812ef2befbee7cce907ef97e7f2e7bde7ba02e7ec00e86fef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81f2",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我自己也搞不清楚！是高达对某种东西、{00}产生了反应……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb5e8c9e7c0ec1ce7b5e995ebd3ef97e7b6e812ef2be7beeae8e7d1e8bae7f80200ec05ef8de7bae87ce87309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x822f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……反应？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e87ce873050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8289",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "外面似乎正在交战",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f7e862e944e933ef3bef29e861ef280000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82b8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "会是友军吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e2e7b6e960e7e0e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82de",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也不清楚",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7c0e7b5e995ebd30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82e9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、待在外围区块、是很危险的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602eaa8ef29e8f7e9deef35ec1002e7b6e981e935e932e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8300",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们往深处走吧",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe911eb0de903e890e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8328",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请、请留步、迪安娜大人！里头说不定、{00}还藏着什么危险……",
   "zh_hex": "15e83a02e83ae98cea9302ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2ef97ef31e92ee7ede7b5e8670200e7f7ed03e86de7dde7bde935e93209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8362",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、没有危险、这里的构造、我了然于心",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7d8e7cbe935e93202e7b9ef31e7b4ece3e93e02efcce7bae7efe879e82d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8397",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83b9",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恐怕、是在时空移动之际、被一并卷了进{00}来吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb33e95802e7b6ef29ef2de93fec83ef30e7cdedc302e7f1efb6e957ecbae7bae89200efcfe7d009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83d6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这里是米斯尔托、对索雷尔家的人而{00}言、是个有渊源的地方",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9ef31e7b6e878e7c8e7e1e7f402e7bee93ce8afe7e1e7dfe7b4b4e89c009b02e7b6e828e7cbef86ebd6e7b4bfd0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x840d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "米斯尔托……是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e878e7c8e7e1e7f40909e7b6e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8435",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在月之民大迁徙的那个时代……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e850e7cdef38efa5eeb3ee1ce7b4e7b7e828ef2de8e709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8445",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了再生空气与食粮、索雷尔家、曾在这{00}里进行过农业实验",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae80bb6e93fe8ede832edc9ee7e02e93ce8afe7e1e7df02ea2aef29e7b900ef31e8929fef36ef7aeadae87fea9900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8478",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……走吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e890e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8483",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要去到深处、说不定就能让动力恢复过{00}来",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7ebe7d7eb0de90302e7ede7b5e867e7c5e7c6e7f9ef30efb0ec69e9eeef3600efcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84e6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这就是所谓的新人类、对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7c5e7b6e7fbe92be7b4ef8aefb2e84102e7bee7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84f8",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这个、我已经『记住』了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e82802efccef3ae8b70ce996e8590de7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x853b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x856a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8572",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……原来你还在啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8e4efcfe7b8e7f7ef29e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85a6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85ce",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感觉到一股有趣的力量、便过来瞧瞧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8aee7d787edace7cbea82e7b4dae85102e8faef36d9ead4ead409090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85e2",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "结果什么嘛、不过是个赝品摆在这儿罢了",
   "zh_hex": "15e868e871e7dde7bde93602e7b5ef36e7b6e828eea8eae1eb8bef29e7b9eb7ceaefe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x861a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基姆·金卡拉姆……你为何、会出现在这{00}种地方……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e8230909e7b8e7c1efbc02e7e2efbee82fef29e7b900e7d1ef63efb10909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8633",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在如今这个时机采取行动、可没有半点好{00}处可言……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7f0efb9e7b9e828ef2de7e4ec9ee987efd6ef3002e7c4e7d8e7cbeadee822e7c700e903e7c4efd709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x866a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼、我可不会听你的指使！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b302efcce7c4e7b5e7e2e8d1e7b8e7b4e8c0e83fef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86a2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起这个……原来如此、那就是你们一直{00}交战的对手吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b9e8280909e8e4d9e7f0e7ca02e7b7e7c5e7b6e7b8e7bb87e87500e861ef28e7b4e7beaee8020000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86be",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……看来、是个相当有意思的对手呢",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7f6efcf02e7b6e828e8b1ef53e7cbef3cefcae7b4e7beef66e9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86fa",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正配得上我们金卡拉姆一族、初阵的开场{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bea34e80aef4cefcce7bbe902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5e02eb4feb48e7b4e7fae87600ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x873a",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基姆·金卡拉姆！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e823ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x875f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈、原来你、也会发出那样的声音啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e802e8e4efcfe7b802e7c0e7e2e870efbee7b7e7dae7b4ea8aea71e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8799",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87bb",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我说过了、我不会听你的指使",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7edef36e7ba02efcce7b5e7e2e8d1e7b8e7b4e8c0e83f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87ce",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还是说、你想让我用倒X、把那艘叫百夫{00}长的玩意儿轰飞？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7b6e7ed02e7b8e7e6e7f9efccefb3e848eed902e81be7b7eb18e8c1ebdce83000ef34e7b4e970ef3ceb7ceefcea45050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x880c",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…………！",
   "zh_hex": "1509090909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x883a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x885c",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "似乎还有一部分敌方部队、残留在此？",
   "zh_hex": "15e944e933e7f7e7cbefb6ef70efaee7e3efb1ef70e7c902e97be98cef29e7ca050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x888c",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无妨、正好拿来当个热身的对手",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce97f02ef3be7c7e9a7efcfef53e828ead1e88de7b4e7beef660000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x88ad",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……基姆·金卡拉姆、出击！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e82302efbee7ccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x88e2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……倒X！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e848eed9ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x890b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈！这不是哈利·奥德嘛！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e806e7b9e7b5e7b6e7e8e82e04e82be82ce9360606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8921",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没想到你、竟在那种地方晃来晃去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7e6e7d7e7b802ef2cef29e7b7e7d1ef63efb1ec20efcfec20e7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8953",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这到底是怎么回事、金卡拉姆！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb802e902e801e7c2e823ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8960",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆一族……你们的舰队、明明该被{00}封存了才对！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5e0909e7b8e7bbe7b4e7d4e7c902ef39ef39e898e7f100eb83e993e7bae836e7beef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x897e",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "未经迪安娜大人许可便擅自出击、竟还搬{00}出了倒X！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b4e8b7ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2e8a7e7c4e8faeb5defb5efbee7cc02ef2ce7f7ecdd00efbee7bae848eed9ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x89b8",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因斗争的时代已拉开序幕、我们才得以{00}登上前台！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7ffe852e7b4ef2de8e7ef3ae7c2e7faeb56ec1402efcce7bbe836e80ae7f300e9a0ef4cef51ea16ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x89db",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们金卡拉姆一族、是执掌武力的家族！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5e02e7b6e9fceb36e8ecefb0e7b4e7dfeb5eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x89ee",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用不着事事去请示那些不懂战争的索雷尔{00}家和门提纳家！",
   "zh_hex": "15d8e7b5e86da9a9e7ebe83aeab0e7b7e8a4e7b5e8b0ef28e852e7b4e93ce8afe7e100e7dfe7d3e90ce821e882e7df06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a36",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对！就是这个……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef97e7c5e7b6e7b9e8280909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a44",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这股力量……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9edacdae8510909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a4c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈哈哈哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a7e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82a0909060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8aa9",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是月光蝶！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6e850e83dea0306060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ada",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b0a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "月光蝶有反应了！哈哈哈、好啊、好兄弟{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e850e83dea03e7cbe87ce873e7baef97e7e8e7e8e7e802e7c7e7c302e7c7ebb5eb8400ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b4e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈、果然不出我所料！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e802e871e7efe7b5efbeefcce7fbeb8cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b60",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就知道、若是你们、定能唤醒这台倒X{00}的月光蝶！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7c5e85ae82a02e7e7e7b6e7b8e7bb02e867e7c6ec0eeb20e7b9ea16e848eed900e7b4e850e83dea030600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ba0",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基姆·金卡拉姆！这就是你的目的吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e823ef97e7b9e7c5e7b6e7b8e7b4efd4e7b4e802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8bd1",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "斗争的时代、就此拉开序幕！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ffe852e7b4ef2de8e702e7c5e7cae7c2e7faeb56ec14ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8be5",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总有一天、我会在相称的大舞台上、与你{00}们一决高下！",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cbefb6e84402efcce7e2ef29e8b1ea01e7b4efa5eb9eea16ef4c02e832e7b800e7bbefb6e8abe812ef4def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c04",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈哈哈哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c36",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……可恶、基姆·金卡拉姆……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7c4e7de02e829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e8230909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c6e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哟、好兄弟！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb2c02e7c7ebb5eb84ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c95",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "兄弟！？我根本就不认识你这个人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ebb5eb84ef9705efcce9b8efa6e7c5e7b5e8a0e92fe7b8e7b9e828efb2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8cc9",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈！称兄弟的、是这两台MS啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ea01ebb5eb84e7b402e7b6e7b9e97dea16efa7ef9ee7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8cdf",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这台倒X和∀高达、是在黑历史中交过手{00}的、一对兄弟啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ea16e848eed9e7d3effee812ef2b02e7b6ef29ef3ee8fbe925ef4ee861ef36ef6600e7b402efb6e7beebb5eb84e7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d18",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这台∀高达、和那台倒X……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ea16effee812ef2b02e7d3e7b7ea16e848eed90909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d4e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "改投了迪安娜回归军、就摆出一副忠义嘴{00}脸吗、哈利·奥德！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f0e948e7baea11e7fce7ea8ce947e7e002e7c5eb8baf87ecb6ec18e8ceeae200eb69e80202e7e8e82e04e82be82c060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d6e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这毫无操守的家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9ea0ae7dceac7e8a8e7b4e7dfe7fdef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d97",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毫无操守的、明明是你们才对吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea0ae7dceac7e8a8e7b402ef39ef39e7b6e7b8e7bbe836e7bee7d0ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8da9",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因你们这种逢谁都打、不分敌我的德行{00}、我才舍弃了金卡拉姆一族！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7b8e7bbe7b9e7d1ed11e923e840e7f502e7b5efaee7e3efcce7b4e82cefd60002efcce836eb17e938e7bae902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8df2",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、区区一群民兵！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302ef35ef35efb6ecfaef38ef93ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e01",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就让你们见识见识、我们演习了两千五百{00}年的武门之力！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7f9e7b8e7bbe85ce92fe85ce92f02efcce7bbea2feab6e7bae97deafdedd2ebdc00e909e7b4e8ece90ce7cdefb0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e41",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这边也不甘示弱！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e899e7c0e7b5ecedeab0e9d1ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e4a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是模拟训练的时长、克莉丝可一点都不{00}输人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6ea91ebc9ec3ceb13e7b4ef2def3402e7d5e81ee8a3e7c487e822e840e7b500e8b9b4060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e7f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等一下、巴尼！！哪有你这么说『光是』{00}的！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e826efb6ef4d02e85be896ef97ef97e8ffe7cbe7b8e7b9e7bde7ed0ce83de7b60d00e7b4ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ebf",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、抱、抱歉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e92202e922e92709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ef2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……大小姐！请您别太莽撞冒进了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa5e83ee921ef97e83ae835e7e5e86aedb2ecdfeb7fe892e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f09",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对手可是月之民里头、专司武力的那帮人{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef66e7c4e7b6e850e7cdef38ef31e92e02eb4beafee8ecefb0e7b4e7b7e910efb200ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f20",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们的身手和装备、跟迪安娜回归军根本{00}不是一个档次！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe7b4e88def66e7d3e98fe87702e973ea11e7fce7eaef52e947e7e0e9b8efa600e7b5e7b6efb6e828ed78e864ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f5b",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那又怎样！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8f1e7f2e7daef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f64",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "载具上的那点差距、靠一股拼劲补回来不{00}就行了！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb1dea14ef4ce7b4e7b7e822e9c7ea0f02e8c7efb6edacea66eb50ea81ef52efcfe7b500e7c5efd6e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fa6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唉、真是的……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5d02e820e7b6e7b40909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fb2",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球上的人、为什么一个个都这么胡来啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef63efd3ef4ce7b4efb202e7c1e7dde7bdefb6e828e828e840e7b9e7bdec8befcfe7c300ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ff2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是说、要我扮成迪安娜、去接近那个{00}叫阿格里帕的人、是吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7ed02ef2aefccec70e837ea11e7fce7ea02e7ebefceefd8e7b7e82800e8c1e7d2e824ef31eb01e7b4efb202e7b6e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x902c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不仅放出了金卡拉姆一族、连倒X都放到{00}世上的阿格里帕……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5eb7ae86cefbee7bae902e801e7c2e823efb6eb5e02e86ee848eed9e840e86ce7d700e83cef4ce7b4e7d2e824ef31eb0109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9047",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "实在不能再放任他下去了、琪耶尔·海姆{00}小姐",
   "zh_hex": "15e87fef29e7b5e7c6e80be86ce89ae80cef4de7ebe7ba02efa1ea31e7e1ef4be91be82300e83ee9210000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x907a",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉、您是打算和他同归于尽吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec08602e835e7b6e7f5e889e7d3e80ce85de947e879e8f2e7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90d0",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我、是喜欢哈利大人您的",
   "zh_hex": "1509098b02e7b6ecc0ea92e7e8e82ebeb4e835e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90e2",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要您肯对我说一句喜欢、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae835e93de7beefcce7edefb6ebb9ecc0ea92020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90f7",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕是去暗杀那个叫阿格里帕的人、我也{00}照样办得到",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958e7b6e7ebea6ae89be7b7e828e8c1e7d2e824ef31eb01e7b4efb202efcce7c000ea1ae7dae8eae80ae7d70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9130",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "琪耶尔·海姆……无论您如何戏弄我、都{00}无妨",
   "zh_hex": "15efa1ea31e7e104e91be8230909e7dce8dce835e7f08aea3eeac48b02e84000e7dce97f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9169",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您就是、不肯对我说吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c5e7b602e7b5e93de7beefcce7ede802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9195",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我希望您、能成为迪安娜大人的盾",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce87be965e83502e7c6e837e7c1ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2e7b4eb630000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x91ad",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若以爱来作为回报、那未免太廉价了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7f3e8d5d9ef2fe7c18ce91302e7b7e8b4eb7de86ae667eb25e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x91e5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈利中尉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e82ec086090900000000"
  }
 ]
}
